Headstrong's mirror images all shifted with the original. That punch 
came way to close for his compfort. "Your legend does you to much 
credit *snort* coward" he spat, swinging his sword in another arc.

-----------------------------------------------------------
Firedril was visibly suprised at what First Aid said, and he looked at 
him funny.
